  "prompt": "Can we load money in multi wallet ICICI card?",
  "response": "Yes, you can load money onto an ICICI multi-wallet card. Here are a few ways to do so:\n\n1. Online Banking\n- Log into your ICICI net banking\n- Go to the multi-wallet section\n- Select 'Add Money' option\n- Choose payment method (debit card, net banking, etc.)\n- Enter the amount you want to load\n\n2. Mobile Banking App\n- Open ICICI mobile banking app\n- Navigate to multi-wallet section\n- Select 'Add Money'\n- Choose payment method\n- Complete transaction\n\n3. ATM\n- Visit ICICI ATM\n- Select 'Add Money to Wallet' option\n- Follow on-screen instructions\n\n4. ICICI Branch\n- Visit nearest ICICI bank branch\n- Request wallet money loading\n- Provide necessary details\n\nTypical loading methods include:\n- Debit card\n- Net banking\n- Credit card\n- Cash deposit\n\nRemember:\n- There might be transaction charges\n- Check maximum wallet loading limit\n- Verify KYC compliance\n- Ensure sufficient funds in source account\n\nFor specific details and current procedures, it's best to directly contact ICICI bank or check their official website.",
